{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775868752703,"sessionID":"ses_285fc3c06ffeoaHprEVR40sEpf","part":{"id":"prt_d7a06b2eb001nkZNjZGQSWhQWX","messageID":"msg_d7a064b920019u13Dwy0xaefaB","sessionID":"ses_285fc3c06ffeoaHprEVR40sEpf","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-a87052b7205b445fbbda4896908db456","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-020 — CLI pack 命令\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-020 — CLI pack 命令 |\n| Module | `cmd/cli` |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\nImplement the `pack` command for the AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`). The pack command:\n\n1. Validates workspace directory structure\n2. Loads or creates `agent_metadata.yaml` (with fallback to `agent.yaml`, `metadata.yaml`)\n3. Merges CLI option overrides into metadata\n4. Validates language compatibility (Python requires `.py` files, Java requires `pom.xml`)\n5. Processes dependencies (Python: requirements.txt; Java: pom.xml)\n6. Generates Dockerfile if missing (language-specific templates)\n7. Updates and saves metadata with pack results\n8. Reports agent_name, workspace_path, metadata_path, dockerfile_path\n\n## Out of Scope\n\n- Docker image building (handled by `build` command - AR-021)\n- Kubernetes deployment (handled by `publish` command - AR-022)\n- Agent invocation (handled by `invoke` command - AR-023)\n- Status checking (handled by `status` command - AR-024)\n- Container registry operations\n- Cloud build mode integration\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n|------------|---------|---------|\n| `typer[all]` | >=0.9.0 | CLI framework with Rich integration |\n| `pydantic` | >=2.0.0 | Metadata model validation |\n| `pyyaml` | >=6.0 | YAML metadata file handling |\n| `rich` | >=13.0.0 | Progress indicators and colored output |\n| `pytest` | >=7.4.0 | Unit/integration testing |\n| `pytest-mock` | >=3.11.0 | Mocking support for tests |\n\n## Deliverables\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer `pack` command implementation |\n| `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | `PackRuntime` class with pack workflow |\n| `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | `MetadataOptions` dataclass |\n| `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | `AgentMetadata` model, `MetadataService` |\n| `tests/test_pack_runtime.py` | PackRuntime unit tests |\n| `tests/test_pack_cli.py` | CLI pack command tests |\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `kubectl-agentcube pack -f /path/to/workspace` validates workspace structure\n- [ ] Creates `agent_metadata.yaml` if missing, loads from fallback files if present\n- [ ] CLI options (`--agent-name`, `--language`, `--entrypoint`, `--port`, `--build-mode`, `--description`) override metadata values\n- [ ] Python workspace validation: requires at least one `.py` file\n- [ ] Java workspace validation: requires `pom.xml`\n- [ ] Generates Dockerfile if missing, preserves existing Dockerfile\n- [ ] Python Dockerfile template: `FROM python:3.10-slim`, pip install, expose port\n- [ ] Java Dockerfile template: Multi-stage Maven build → JRE runtime\n- [ ] Saves updated metadata to `{workspace}/agent_metadata.yaml`\n- [ ] Rich progress spinner during pack operation\n- [ ] Success output: agent_name, workspace_path, metadata_path, dockerfile_path\n- [ ] Error output: colored error message, traceback if --verbose, exit code 1\n- [ ] Port validation: 1-65535 range\n- [ ] Language validation: 'python' or 'java' only\n- [ ] Build mode validation: 'local' or 'cloud' only\n\n## References\n\n- cli-toolkit/design.md — CLI toolkit architecture\n- cli-toolkit/spec.md — CLI specification\n- AR-021 — CLI build command\n- AR-022 — CLI publish command\n- AR-023 — CLI invoke command\n- AR-024 — CLI status command","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-020/spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-020/spec.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-020/spec.md","time":{"start":1775868752693,"end":1775868752701}}}}
